Welcome to your new
home sweet home.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.100
Well, it's just us now.

00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:11.966
Oh. And them.

00:00:11.966 --> 00:00:15.133
Ain't ya gonna come say hi?

00:00:15.133 --> 00:00:17.333
Uh, yeah, we were
just about to.

00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:18.600
Too late!

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.200
Gong says leave
those four alone!

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:24.133
No way, for real?
Gong is that‐‐

00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:26.300
Yuya, so good to see you!

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:29.066
Guess any friend of Yuya
is a friend of ours.

00:00:29.066 --> 00:00:31.100
I suppose that would
include me, then.

00:00:31.100 --> 00:00:32.200
Dennis.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.566
Tokumatsu runs this joint.

00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:40.166
If you want no trouble,
then hand over your cards.

00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:41.400
(Yuya)
Or what?

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.066
Or face the wrath
of Tokumatsu!

00:00:43.066 --> 00:00:44.433
No, never!

00:00:44.433 --> 00:00:45.666
Let's duel!
Let's duel!

00:00:45.666 --> 00:00:49.000
I Synchro Summon!

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.466
Level 8 Flower Cardian
Lightshower!

00:00:55.366 --> 00:00:57.900
Turn up the heat, Odd‐Eyes
Pendulum Dragon!

00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.700
(roaring)

00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:03.233
See‐saw to it, Peformapal Teeter
Totter Hopper!

00:01:03.233 --> 00:01:06.733
Crawl to victory,
Peformapal Sellshell Crab!

00:01:06.733 --> 00:01:09.400
I'm activating the trap card
Fraud Freeze,

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.433
so all of your monster's
will be gone!

00:01:11.433 --> 00:01:14.433
Oh, no!

00:01:14.433 --> 00:01:16.766
Perhaps now you finally
understand

00:01:16.766 --> 00:01:19.266
that power
is everything, Yuya.

00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:21.466
The worst is yet to come!

00:01:21.466 --> 00:01:24.300
(sinister laugh)

00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:27.133
♪

00:01:32.133 --> 00:01:35.066
♪ Hey, hey,
Can you feel the power? ♪

00:01:35.066 --> 00:01:37.666
♪ You vs. me,
Competition for the victory ♪

00:01:37.666 --> 00:01:40.133
♪ I could be the best one day
and make history ♪

00:01:40.133 --> 00:01:42.500
♪ Swing into action,
Are you ready to play? ♪

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:45.200
