♪ Activate the spell,
Let your powers come to life ♪

00:01:53.033 --> 00:01:56.033
♪ It's showtime,
Who will win the fight? ♪

00:01:56.033 --> 00:02:01.433
♪ I'm ready to duel,
Go 'head and make your move ♪

00:02:01.433 --> 00:02:04.466
♪ I'll win this duel,
You can't beat my moves ♪

